      {
        "Language": "JPN",
        "Name": "\u89AA\u7766\u6DF1\u307E\u308B\u56E3\u4F53\u6226",
        "Client": "\u738B\u56FD\u9A0E\u58EB\u30B8\u30A7\u30A4",
        "Description": "\u003CPL\u003E\u3055\u3093\u3068\r\n\u5E2B\u5320\u3067\u3042\u308B\u30A6\u30C4\u30B7\u6559\u5B98\u306E\u72E9\u731F\u3092\r\n\u9593\u8FD1\u3067\u898B\u3089\u308C\u308B\u306A\u3093\u3066\u3001\u3053\u3093\u306A\r\n\u6A5F\u4F1A\u3001\u6EC5\u591A\u306B\u3042\u308B\u3082\u3093\u3058\u3083\u306A\u3044\r\n\u3067\u3059\u3088\uFF01\u3000\u305F\u3068\u3048\u5012\u308C\u3088\u3046\u3068\u3001\r\n\u4E8C\u4EBA\u306E\u52C7\u59FF\u3001\u3057\u3063\u304B\u308A\u3053\u306E\u76EE\u306B\r\n\u713C\u304D\u4ED8\u3051\u3055\u305B\u3066\u3044\u305F\u3060\u304D\u307E\u3059\uFF01",
        "Target": "\u5168\u3066\u306E\u30BF\u30FC\u30B2\u30C3\u30C8\u306E\u72E9\u731F",
        "Fail": "\u5831\u916C\u91D1\u30BC\u30ED\r\n\u30BF\u30A4\u30E0\u30A2\u30C3\u30D7"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Front Row Seat",
        "Client": "Sir Jae",
        "Description": "It\u0027s not every day you get a chance\r\nto see two masters at work! I\u0027m so\r\nstoked to hunt with you and Master\r\nUtsushi! I promise I won\u0027t miss a\r\nsingle moment, even if it\u0027s from a\r\ncart as Felynes wheel me back to\r\ncamp! This is gonna be awesome!",
        "Target": "Hunt all target monsters",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Aux premi\u00E8res loges",
        "Client": "Sieur Jae",
        "Description": "J\u0027ai rarement l\u0027occasion de te\r\nvoir chasser avec Ma\u00EEtre\r\nUtsushi de si pr\u00E8s ! Je ne\r\nvais pas en rater une miette,\r\nm\u00EAme si je dois ouvrir\r\nl\u0027\u0153il depuis ma civi\u00E8re en\r\n\u00E9tant rapatri\u00E9 au camp !",
        "Target": "Chasser tous les monstres",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Chi caccia insieme",
        "Client": "Sir Jae",
        "Description": "Non capita spesso di vedere\r\nsia te che il maestro Utsushi\r\nall\u0027opera cos\u00EC da vicino. Non\r\nmi perder\u00F2 un solo istante,\r\ndovessi pure guardarvi da\r\nuna barella mentre i gatti\r\nmi riportano in tenda.",
        "Target": "Caccia tutti i mostri assegnati",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Mittendrin statt nur dabei",
        "Client": "Sir Jae",
        "Description": "Ich habe nicht oft die Gelegen-\r\nheit, zwei Meister bei der Arbeit\r\nzu sehen, deshalb bin ich so auf-\r\ngeregt, mit dir und Utsushi jagen zu\r\ngehen! Ich werde keinen Moment\r\nverpassen, nicht einmal vom Wagen\r\nder Felynen auf dem Weg ins Lager!",
        "Target": "Erjage alle Zielmonster.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "En primera fila",
        "Client": "Jae",
        "Description": "\u00A1Pocas veces se tiene ocasi\u00F3n\r\nde ver a dos maestros en acci\u00F3n!\r\n\u00A1Qu\u00E9 ganas de cazar contigo\r\ny el maestro Utsushi! Apreciar\u00E9\r\ncada momento, \u00A1hasta a los\r\nFelyne llev\u00E1ndome en carreta!\r\n\u00A1Va a ser genial!",
        "Target": "Caza todos los objetivos",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0422\u0435, \u043A\u0442\u043E \u043E\u0445\u043E\u0442\u044F\u0442\u0441\u044F \u0432\u043C\u0435\u0441\u0442\u0435",
